ve me,"],[2915,3028,"I'll call her right now."],[3028,3107,"The reason I was carrying..."],[3107,3165,"Just go!"],[3336,3436,"Maybe,"],[3495,3699,"there was a small part of me"],[3757,3924,"that wanted to forgive you."],[4575,4688,"But now..."],[4867,5050,"Now that the babies are gone,"],[5138,5526,"there is nothing left between us."],[5935,6151,"Nina please, don't..."],[6151,6356,"I can't lose you..."],[6510,6598,"The babies..."],[6806,6936,"They may be gone,"],[7127,7232,"But I'm still here."],[7232,7361,"You still have me."],[7745,7841,"If you don't believe me,"],[7841,7916,"I'll call her."],[7920,8091,"I'm gonna call her right now."],[8229,8395,"I'll make her tell you."],[8717,8892,"Candice, Nina has the"],[8892,9059,"wrong idea about us."],[9154,9325,"Please come here right now,"],[9330,9626,"just tell her the truth."],[9655,9772,"Tell her that there's"],[9772,9926,"nothing going on between us."]],"28":[[179,387,"She's on her way, just"],[387,588,"just listen to her you'll"],[588,796,"see I'm telling the truth."],[1351,1589,"You just got out of the hospital."],[1634,1718,"Come here sit."],[1718,1885,"No, don't touch me."],[2010,2118,"Your hands..."],[2260,2339,"they're cold, yeah,"],[2339,2435,"I could, I could,"],[2435,2556,"turn up the heat or"],[2556,2740,"or the iron supplements"],[2740,2911,"that you used to take,"],[2911,3073,"you need to regain"],[3073,3186,"your strength."],[3194,3357,"I'll get them."],[3357,3465,"It's too late Easton!"],[3465,3628,"No it's not!"],[3812,3974,"Hey no."],[4137,4287,"We found the trial lead."],[4416,4567,"After this last phase"],[4587,4688,"we'll have the side"],[4688,4788,"effects documented,"],[4788,4979,"we’ll perfect the formula,"],[4979,5159,"you won't need surgery,"],[5159,5334,"your birthmark will be gone"],[5334,5505,"and everything will be okay!"],[5505,5680,"So that's what it was!"],[5818,6168,"You've always hated my face!"],[6406,6539,"My birthmark,"],[6927,7044,"tell me Easton,"],[7136,7290,"was it her work ethic that"],[7290,7615,"drew you in? Or her clean,"],[7636,7807,"flawless face?"],[7845,7991,"The one that looks like mine"],[7991,8170,"except without the Mark?"],[8525,8608,"Easton?"],[8666,8804,"What's going on?"],[8804,8979,"You sounded kind of frantic."],[8979,9088,"You gave her the"],[9088,9205,"code to our house?"],[9405,9551,"I really don't remember"],[9551,9647,"agreeing to that."]],"29":[[629,709,"Candice,"],[796,955,"perfect timing, can you tell"],[955,1080,"Nina that there's nothing"],[1080,1176,"going on between us?"],[1176,1368,"Between me and Easton? I mean..."],[1618,1847,"Oh my goodness, Nina!"],[1901,2043,"Your stomach, did you"],[2043,2164,"already give birth?"],[2235,2339,"Candice I brought"],[2339,2435,"you here to help,"],[2460,2523,"not ask questions"],[2523,2581,"that are"],[2581,2656,"none of your business."],[2656,2773,"Okay okay."],[2894,3073,"But let me talk to her,"],[3073,3199,"just the two of us."],[3319,3395,"You being here"],[3395,3507,"really isn't helping."],[3507,3687,"Maybe go find her favorite"],[3687,3807,"snack or something."],[3899,3978,"Nina,"],[4029,4195,"I'll be right back okay?"],[4416,4537,"Bye!"],[4767,4879,"So did you file the"],[4879,4988,"divorce papers yet?"],[5009,5096,"You might want to"],[5096,5196,"keep that sweet girl"],[5196,5359,"act up a little longer,"],[5367,5463,"he's probably still"],[5463,5538,"in the driveway."],[5547,5697,"Oh please,"],[5709,5885,"Easton trusts me,"],[5955,6118,"he left you with me for a reason."],[6118,6260,"He's not coming"],[6260,6414,"back in. -Oh really?"],[6506,6648,"You wanna know where he was"],[6648,6781,"while you were screaming"],[6781,6927,"in that hospital bed?"],[7098,7228,"With me."],[7315,7428,"And every time he"],[7428,7590,"thought about calling you..."],[7665,7807,"I kissed him."],[7857,8045,"And just like that, he"],[8045,8295,"forgot all about little Nina."],[8395,8687,"We were either eating,"],[8687,9017,"or hooking up everywhere,"],[9017,9146,"different places,"],[9146,9288,"all sorts of ways."],[9501,9576,"Bet he was never like"],[9576,9655,"that with you though."],[9655,9734,"Was he?"],[9797,9947,"Easton's considerate."],[10005,10118,"He's always cared"],[10118,10231,"about my feelings."],[10247,10443,"Yeah, and that's probably"],[10443,10614,"why he cheated on you."]],"30":[[0,166,"So what, you just bring out"],[166,296,"the sex crazed animal in him,"],[296,487,"is that it? And what"],[487,671,"does that make you?"],[738,809,"His little"],[809,925,"stress relief toy?"],[938,1217,"You bitch! Face it,"],[1230,1355,"you've already lost!"],[1422,1493,"Back then maybe"],[1493,1568,"the twins were the only"],[1568,1659,"reason Easton stuck around,"],[1659,1801,"but now..."],[1856,1981,"what do you have left?"],[2043,2160,"Candice Black."],[2314,2686,"I was this close"],[2686,2890,"to letting you have him."],[2961,3203,"But the one thing you never"],[3203,3349,"should have messed with"],[3349,3520,"is my children!"],[3520,3707,"What are you talking about?"],[3707,3828,"I didn't do anything"],[3828,3920,"to your children."],[3987,4141,"And who knows, with how often"],[4141,4262,"Easton and I were at it,"],[4262,4412,"maybe I'm pregnant now."],[4466,4537,"Maybe I'll be the one"],[4537,4604,"to give him a child"],[4604,4813,"to heal his broken heart."],[4813,4942,"Oh, he'll be a dadagain. -God!"],[4942,5038,"Real soon."],[5038,5113,"Candice!"],[5196,5355,"You've got money, you've got looks,"],[5355,5467,"you've got charm!"],[5576,5676,"So why?"],[5768,6022,"Why chase after a married man?"],[6135,6331,"Why beg to be the other woman?"],[6398,6489,"Easton's one of the"],[6489,6585,"youngest billionaires"],[6585,6664,"in the country."],[6769,6977,"A man like him?"],[6977,7194,"you don't wait for a chance..."],[7244,7407,"you take it."],[7407,7503,"And when Easton finds out"],[7503,7611,"that you were the one"],[7611,7732,"that lured me to Honolulu,"],[7745,7824,"and that you"],[7824,7937,"staged everything"],[7962,8124,"just so I would find out."],[8208,8375,"And that you knew..."],[8425,8558,"that I was that pregnant"],[8558,8666,"woman on that flight"],[8666,8804,"that the flight attendant"],[8804,8904,"was screaming about!"],[8942,9104,"And you just dragged him away."],[9104,9234,"When he finds out all of that"],[9234,9305,"you think he's"],[9305,9413,"still gonna want you?"]],"31":[[0,266,"So what, you've got proof?"],[279,437,"You know what? Fine."],[467,558,"I'll give it to you."],[558,671,"You covered your tracks,"],[671,788,"congratulations."],[788,905,"You know what then honey?"],[946,1197,"No proof, no truth."],[1205,1301,"Easton's never"],[1301,1447,"going to believe you."],[1455,1576,"I'm his most valuable"],[1576,1668,"business partner."],[1685,1851,"Even if he doubts me,"],[1851,2047,"he'll never cut me loose."],[2335,2469,"That's for me!"],[2610,2769,"That's for my children!"],[2886,3098,"And that is for the hate"],[3098,3319,"that I will carry for you"],[3319,3549,"for the rest of my life..."],[3695,3841,"Enough! what does"],[3841,4058,"hitting me even get you?"],[4058,4245,"Let me tell you something, Nina."],[4245,4475,"I was too soft before."],[4475,4808,"Too... damn... nice."],[4817,4913,"If I'd broken you"],[4913,4988,"two up earlier,"],[4988,5146,"those little bastards would"],[5146,5280,"have never even existed."],[5380,5476,"What?"],[5534,5755,"Who the hell are you calling"],[5755,5822,"bastards?"],[5822,5876,"Easton!"]],"32":[[0,233,"Easton when did you get back?"],[396,504,"I never left."],[504,596,"It’s not what it looks like,"],[596,696,"please I can explain..."],[696,779,"Shut up!"],[888,988,"I trusted you."],[1088,1159,"You've been"],[1159,1234,"playing both sides,"],[1234,1384,"turning Nina against me"],[1384,1505,"behind my back."],[1718,1797,"Nina,"],[1830,2027,"don't listen to a word she says."],[2031,2122,"That night in"],[2122,2264,"Honolulu, I was drunk."],[2264,2356,"It was a mistake."],[2356,2498,"You're the only woman"],[2498,2648,"I've ever cared about."],[2669,2769,"God Easton,"],[2769,2886,"every word you say right"],[2886,3015,"now makes me wanna throw up."],[3015,3161,"You're mad at me, I deserve it."],[3161,3315,"You you wanna yell at me,"],[3315,3395,"do it."],[3499,3628,"But she pushed this."],[3687,3991,"She lied to you. She lied to me."],[4095,4229,"And she's gonna say it."],[4291,4358,"Say it?"],[4396,4617,"Say what? Apologize to her?"],[4617,4704,"Not a chance."],[4704,4775,"Candice Black!"],[4775,4921,"Don't yell at me!"],[4921,5088,"You and I had something real,"],[5088,5171,"don't pretend you"],[5171,5238,"didn't feel it."],[5238,5409,"The only woman I’ve"],[5409,5568,"ever loved is Nina."],[5618,5734,"You're lying."],[6026,6139,"You can lie to her but"],[6139,6247,"don't lie to yourself."],[6456,6627,"When you looked at me,"],[6719,6886,"the way you touched me,"],[7044,7111,"you haven't felt"],[7111,7178,"that way about her,"],[7178,7286,"not in a long time,"],[7286,7378,"and you know it."],[7565,7799,"You don't seem to get it, do you?"],[7899,8037,"I said shut up."]],"33":[[16,208,"What are you so afraid of?!"],[258,446,"You don't love her anymore,"],[446,567,"stop pretending"],[567,700,"that you still do!"],[709,871,"You don't owe her anything!"],[900,1030,"Let's get one thing straight."],[1109,1330,"I only trusted you because"],[1330,1484,"you looked like her."],[1676,1876,"Cause you had a face that"],[1876,2047,"reminded me of Nina's."],[2189,2298,"She's the only woman"],[2298,2381,"I've ever loved."],[2581,2698,"First time we met,"],[2798,2957,"she handed me an umbrella,"],[3078,3186,"told me I didn't have"],[3186,3278,"to walk in the rain."],[3611,3770,"She was the only one that"],[3770,3945,"ever showed me true kindness."],[4058,4191,"And from that day forward,"],[4191,4358,"I promised that I would never"],[4529,4596,"treat her wrong."],[4596,4771,"I would always give"],[4771,4988,"her a life of happiness."],[5117,5271,"And that I would never"],[5476,5634,"make her feel cold again."],[6498,6702,"And yet the worst pain I've"],[6702,6906,"ever felt has come from you."],[6915,6998,"When I told you"],[6998,7102,"the whole world would"],[7102,7228,"mean nothing without you,"],[7228,7298,"I meant it."],[7353,7436,"Just stop,"],[7436,7586,"who are you trying to fool?"],[7657,7749,"Nina please,"],[7778,7907,"I know I let you"],[7907,8045,"down, and I'm sorry."],[8095,8291,"But this woman..."],[8291,8500,"She dragged us into this."],[8566,8725,"And you deserve the truth."],[8808,8942,"She's gonna say it."],[8942,9050,"Are you serious?"],[9180,9317,"I'm your business partner!"],[9317,9388,"You and I make"],[9388,9471,"millions together!"],[9471,9567,"And you're gonna throw"],[9567,9651,"it all away for her?"],[9738,9813,"I can always find"],[9813,9909,"another business partner."],[9909,10068,"But there's only one Nina."],[10176,10347,"How can you do this to me?"],[10397,10514,"Apologize."],[10627,10848,"I said no."]],"34":[[693,773,"Easton..."],[850,913,"Easton stop."],[913,1013,"Stop it, Easton."],[1153,1233,"Nina..."],[1353,1473,"How about now?"],[1600,1710,"Do you feel better?"],[1813,2020,"Ah stop it!"],[2070,2193,"Not enough hey?"],[2413,2493,"Fine."],[2620,2700,"Ah!"],[2993,3163,"Easton stop it!"],[3520,3610,"That's enough!"],[4170,4250,"How about now?"],[4320,4490,"Does the truth come out now?"],[4530,4720,"This won't change anything!"],[4843,4990,"You cheated."],[5240,5363,"Our babies..."],[5440,5590,"Our babies are gone."],[5590,5700,"I know!"],[5780,5870,"I know."],[6183,6283,"Say it."],[6353,6443,"It's me, it's Candice!"],[6443,6523,"Why are you"],[6523,6640,"doing this to me?"],[6640,6803,"I know who you are."],[6980,7133,"A million candices"],[7290,7400,"couldn't replace"],[7400,7540,"one breath from Nina."],[7650,7820,"I said that's enough!"],[7893,7983,"What?"],[8153,8293,"Are you finally happy?"],[8320,8400,"Easton!"],[8443,8693,"It's too late!"],[8693,8910,"All of this? It’s over."],[8980,9113,"Let's leave with"],[9113,9310,"whatever dignity we have."],[9433,9513,"Nina..."],[9663,9820,"please don’t leave you're the"],[9820,9960,"only thing I have left."]],"35":[[23,150,"It's too late."],[220,436,"Do you remember what you"],[436,683,"gave me on our anniversary?"],[1383,1510,"The divorce papers..."],[2860,3020,"No, no,"],[3020,3163,"No no no..."],[3810,3890,"Nina?"],[3980,4140,"The agreement, where is it?"],[4140,4293,"You can't sign it, you can't."],[4300,4423,"That piece of paper"],[4423,4523,"was your promise."],[4560,4810,"Your guarantee six years ago."],[4810,4963,"You gave me that piece of paper"],[4963,5176,"and you told me if"],[5176,5413,"you ever betrayed me,"],[5580,5663,"that you would"],[5663,5770,"leave with nothing."],[5883,6040,"You'll never see me again."],[6103,6250,"Not in this lifetime."]],"36":[[33,113,"Nina..."],[213,326,"Is there really no"],[326,443,"coming back for us?"],[443,603,"You know me. Once"],[603,773,"I make up my mind,"],[820,1043,"no one's changing it."],[1043,1503,"Just tell me, our babies,"],[1520,1650,"where are they?"],[1663,1926,"I buried them. Somewhere that"],[1926,2150,"you will never find them."],[2370,2493,"And honestly?"],[2610,2730,"I don’t think they"],[2730,2870,"wanna see you either."],[2923,3020,"You're right."],[3140,3230,"You're right."],[3460,3540,"Nina..."],[3720,3840,"I never felt"],[3840,4050,"anything real for her."],[4213,4293,"Hey."],[4380,4486,"I'll come and check"],[4486,4600,"on you tomorrow okay?"],[4633,4703,"Take your"],[4703,4803,"mistress with you."],[4803,4980,"She's not my mistress!"],[5043,5240,"I said take her."]],"37":[[196,550,"Okay, I have to do something big,"],[625,759,"something she'll never forget."],[875,946,"Maybe then,"],[946,1038,"she'll forgive me."],[1121,1201,"Boss,"],[1267,1418,"I just found something,"],[1418,1584,"you're not gonna believe this."],[1584,1718,"A few days ago..."],[1760,1931,"Miss..es Jones."],[2006,2127,"She planned a wedding."],[2281,2581,"A wedding? I knew it!"],[2581,2940,"No, I knew she still cared. You know,"],[2961,3094,"Nina and I have been"],[3094,3261,"through so much together,"],[3290,3382,"I always promised"],[3382,3478,"her a big wedding."],[3478,3649,"And here she is planning"],[3649,3778,"one behind my back."],[3795,3874,"You know, maybe,"],[3937,4012,"maybe she wanted"],[4012,4091,"to surprise me, or,"],[4091,4237,"or maybe she's finally"],[4237,4408,"giving me a second chance,"],[4408,4571,"a second chance to"],[4571,4729,"make things right."],[4729,4825,"Do you think,"],[4959,5150,"if you finish setting it up"],[5150,5338,"for her, if you surprise her,"],[5376,5505,"she might forgive you?"],[5555,5768,"It doesn't matter!"],[5768,5968,"I'm gonna do it anyway."],[5980,6139,"Give her the wedding"],[6139,6318,"that she deserves. Oh uh,"],[6339,6439,"the trial lead,"],[6498,6581,"the experimental, how"],[6581,6669,"how is it coming along?"],[6669,6823,"The timeline's locked in,"],[6823,6965,"it could start anytime."],[7228,7390,"Ah perfect haha."],[7507,7699,"But once I clear her birthmark."],[7699,7811,"Once I give her the"],[7811,7937,"face that she deserves."],[8058,8137,"She'll come back to me."],[8137,8600,"She has to. First up wedding venue."],[8700,8867,"You bastard! You froze my"],[8867,8938,"shares, you"],[8938,9054,"stripped me clean!"],[9096,9196,"Is that a problem?"],[9234,9325,"Problem!"],[9351,9534,"You and I built this company"],[9534,9676,"together, every meeting,"],[9676,9801,"every deal. I fucking"],[9801,9934,"bled for this company!"],[9934,10026,"And you think you can"],[10026,10089,"just erase me?"],[10139,10201,"Candice,"],[10235,10497,"let's get one thing clear..."],[10497,10764,"Without me, you're nothing."],[10906,11015,"And for the shares,"],[11056,11169,"consider them a payment"],[11169,11290,"for what you did to Nina."],[11327,11486,"Yeah they're hers now."],[11536,11728,"And as for the part you"],[11728,11945,"had in the death of my kids,"],[12049,12224,"I will come for you."],[12324,12445,"Watch me."]],"38":[[16,87,"Are you really"],[87,158,"gonna do this to me?"],[158,329,"I told you I can't"],[329,529,"stand seeing Nina cry."],[554,721,"You were the one that broke her,"],[729,880,"and it made me the"],[880,1017,"one that hurt her."],[1017,1238,"That's because I love you!"],[1317,1418,"Easton..."],[1484,1576,"If you had stayed"],[1576,1647,"in your lane,"],[1785,1935,"we might have kept the peace."],[2198,2348,"But we both made mistakes,"],[2510,2656,"and it's time to pay for them."],[2715,2865,"So what are you gonna do?"],[2957,3065,"You’ll find out."],[6410,6489,"Martha."],[6669,6798,"How is she, is she eating?"],[6848,6948,"Mr Jones,"],[6981,7102,"I've been giving her the"],[7102,7173,"food and"],[7173,7248,"supplements you sent."],[7290,7403,"She eats a little,"],[7403,7511,"if I beg her but..."],[7511,7670,"But what?"],[7741,7866,"She's barely keeping"],[7866,7945,"anything down."],[7957,8058,"She's so thin now."],[8058,8241,"Mr. Jones she's been"],[8241,8387,"crying non stop."],[8420,8546,"It breaks my heart just"],[8546,8637,"looking at her."],[8637,8867,"Okay just please"],[9017,9125,"don't leave her."],[9288,9417,"Stay with her, okay?"],[9534,9617,"Sir,"],[9697,9780,"why aren't you"],[9780,9880,"staying with her?"],[9918,10060,"Why send food flowers"],[10060,10247,"and vitamins from far away,"],[10289,10472,"when the only thing she"],[10472,10627,"really needs is you?"]],"39":[[73,163,"I..."],[250,410,"I did something terrible."],[500,743,"Mrs. Jones has a kind heart."],[760,933,"If you want her forgiveness,"],[933,1046,"do what you should"],[1046,1163,"have done all along."],[1180,1390,"Show up. Be there."],[1390,1583,"Hold her through it all."],[1583,1780,"She just lost her twins."],[1820,1980,"She doesn't need"],[1980,2190,"flowers, she needs you."],[2390,2513,"She won't leave me."],[2823,2920,"I won't let her."],[4713,4793,"Nina."],[4913,5093,"I miss you so much."],[6520,6610,"What do I have to do"],[6610,6713,"to earn you back?"],[7423,7613,"Easton! Get the hell"],[7613,7820,"away from me! Get out!"]],"40":[[0,75,"Nina don't be scared,"],[75,158,"I'm not gonna hurt you,"],[158,196,"I would never..."],[196,237,"What"],[329,458,"are you doing here?"],[550,775,"I, I brought you cupcakes,"],[800,950,"um your favorite ones"],[950,1063,"from that place on"],[1063,1197,"Melrose that you love."],[1255,1376,"I'm not hungry."],[1468,1539,"Okay, uh,"],[1539,1630,"can I do anything"],[1630,1701,"else for you?"],[1701,1826,"Can I, can I give you a massage?"],[1826,1889,"I'm fine!"],[1926,1985,"Tell me what to do..."],[1985,2156,"I said I'm fine."],[2277,2360,"Tell me what I can do,"],[2360,2419,"I'll do anything."],[2419,2502,"Just tell me."],[2610,2690,"You know what"],[2690,2790,"you can do for me?"],[2877,3011,"Here's what you can do."],[3011,3178,"Get out!"],[3249,3420,"I filed for a divorce."],[3445,3541,"And as for the"],[3541,3687,"agreement you gave me?"],[3724,3908,"This house now belongs to me."],[3945,4058,"You're trespassing."],[4124,4287,"I could call the cops if I want."],[4350,4425,"I've known you"],[4425,4508,"for over a decade,"],[4508,4587,"and you've never"],[4587,4688,"talked to me like that."],[4796,4888,"Do you know what I’ve"],[4888,4959,"been doing lately?"],[5005,5138,"I do."],[5138,5288,"You’ve been planning a wedding."],[5401,5547,"So so Martha told you?"],[5547,5630,"She did."],[5689,5893,"So does, does that"],[5893,6056,"make you happy?"]],"41":[[158,396,"Easton Jones, what the hell"],[396,533,"gives you the right to"],[533,667,"ask me that question?"],[738,884,"Hey I'm sorry Nina. Nina"],[884,1001,"I'm, I'm, I'm so sorry."],[1121,1267,"Do you know what I dreamed of?"],[1355,1576,"From the moment I married you,"],[1618,1735,"I waited."],[1835,1972,"I waited for the day that I"],[1972,2097,"would walk down that aisle"],[2097,2218,"in that white dress."],[2331,2431,"I'd be the happiest"],[2431,2519,"girl in the world."],[2660,2844,"And you took that"],[2844,3090,"dream and you burned it."],[3211,3361,"Can I, can I fix it?"],[3361,3411,"Please..."],[3445,3516,"Fix it?"],[3649,3849,"Every time I see you,"],[3937,4091,"I see you and Candice"],[4091,4266,"gripping each other"],[4266,4429,"in that hotel room."],[4475,4654,"I feel the weight of my"],[4654,4829,"baby's ashes in my arms."],[4900,5226,"‘I'll fix it!’ Happiness Easton?"],[5251,5330,"You don't even"],[5330,5426,"get to say my name."],[5455,5551,"I know."],[5609,5739,"I know, I know."],[5885,6085,"I don't deserve it, but..."],[6281,6548,"but I will wait for you,"],[6548,6781,"forever if I have to,"],[6781,6906,"no matter what you decide."],[7027,7207,"Do you know what what this is?"],[7419,7686,"This is what I owe you."],[7895,7978,"Will you wear this"],[7978,8091,"tomorrow to our wedding?"],[8350,8458,"Our wedding?"],[8537,8658,"One that you were planning,"],[8658,8775,"right, the one you booked?"],[9250,9355,"Just leave it here."],[9517,9680,"So so does that mean that you'll..."],[9680,9805,"Just go!"],[9805,9918,"Sure yeah, okay."],[9918,10001,"Okay um..."],[10035,10135,"I won't bother you anymore."],[10135,10318,"Just stay here."],[10385,10464,"Rest."],[13817,13922,"The dress I waited"],[13922,14047,"my whole life to wear,"],[14439,14577,"is the dress I'll wear to"],[14577,14698,"say goodbye to you, Easton."]],"42":[[66,196,"The dress I've waited"],[196,325,"my whole life to wear,"],[496,629,"is the dress I'll wear to"],[629,754,"say goodbye to you, Easton."],[3516,3628,"I'll come in tomorrow"],[3628,3695,"for the trial."],[4938,5009,"He planned the"],[5009,5096,"whole thing himself?"],[5201,5367,"He must be head over heels."],[5405,5526,"A rich guy who sticks"],[5526,5634,"with his first love?"],[5634,5730,"That's rare."],[5755,5880,"This is the kind of boss"],[5880,6018,"that people actually trust."],[6147,6239,"Nina..."],[6448,6564,"I know you'll come."],[6698,6806,"Walking towards me..."],[6806,6936,"in that wedding dress."],[7144,7236,"We'll be alright."],[7390,7528,"Everything will be OK."]],"43":[[233,367,"Mrs. Jones, you're here."],[367,483,"Let's get started."],[533,696,"Well this is a consent form,"],[696,796,"if you'd like to take a"],[796,900,"few minutes to review it,"],[900,1001,"and then sign, then"],[1001,1105,"we can get started."],[1730,1935,"Are you not going to read this?"],[1951,2206,"No need, I know what it says."],[2273,2394,"Side effects are unknown."],[2515,2702,"But if I take it,"],[2744,2936,"my mark will be gone, right?"],[3011,3240,"That is the promise, yes."]],"44":[[1951,2035,"Easton!"],[2235,2419,"I'm here to marry you."],[2556,2635,"Candice?"],[2748,2911,"What the hell is this?"],[2911,3090,"Nina sent me the dress."],[3136,3261,"She said she finally"],[3261,3457,"understands that we're in love!"],[3478,3691,"She wanted to let go for us."],[3858,4037,"That dress was for Nina,"],[4129,4308,"take it off now!"],[4450,4567,"Take it off! -Easton!"],[4817,5109,"Face it, she's not coming back,"],[5109,5288,"she'll never forgive you."],[5351,5505,"You think I don't know"],[5505,5638,"how stubborn she is?"],[5655,5839,"I knew, but still..."],[5839,6010,"I held hope for..."],[6126,6277,"for a miracle."],[6277,6456,"You don't need a miracle."],[6498,6798,"I love you, I've always loved you."],[6798,6948,"And I've given you more"],[6948,7094,"help than she ever has."],[7165,7365,"I know you love me too!"],[7499,7615,"Who said that?"],[7857,7957,"Hey everyone,"],[8074,8191,"I have an announcement."],[8291,8420,"Because of my"],[8420,8621,"disgraceful behavior,"],[8875,9046,"Nina Jones and I"],[9167,9338,"will be getting a divorce."],[9338,9426,"What?"],[9755,9901,"I'll be transferring all"],[9901,10039,"of my assets to her name."],[10085,10168,"Easton!"],[10226,10377,"Shut the fuck up!"],[10764,11019,"This woman, Candice Black,"],[11131,11223,"is the woman I"],[11223,11336,"had an affair with."]],"45":[[12,262,"This woman, Candice Black"],[375,467,"is the woman I"],[467,583,"had an affair with."],[892,1076,"And after she slept with me,"],[1076,1276,"she tormented my wife."],[1276,1643,"That stress cost us our twins."],[1751,1830,"Yes..."],[1931,2035,"I'm a sinner."],[2173,2335,"I failed as a"],[2335,2594,"father and a husband."],[2731,2902,"But Candice? She knew."],[2902,3082,"And she did it anyway."],[3132,3257,"So I say this to every"],[3257,3382,"business partner here,"],[3432,3553,"wanting to work"],[3553,3703,"with Candice Black..."],[3703,3803,"What are you doing?"],[4033,4191,"You might want to think twice."],[4471,4733,"Homewrecker! You shameless bitch!"],[4775,4833,"No no!"],[4833,4950,"I'm not a mistress, Easton"],[4950,5071,"tell them, please!"],[5426,5643,"Monster! Sinner!"],[5643,5822,"How dare you do that? Sinner!"],[5834,6022,"As for me..."],[6101,6272,"I'll carry this sin to the grave."],[6802,6961,"Boss, bad news..."],[6986,7123,"we just found out,"],[7123,7273,"the person who volunteered"],[7273,7374,"for the drug trial..."],[7394,7624,"It's your wife. It's Nina!"],[7624,7699,"What?"],[7699,7853,"She already took the pill, sir."],[7853,7932,"The one with the"],[7932,8053,"unpredictable side effects."],[8053,8191,"We tracked her location,"],[8224,8387,"she's at the old apartment"],[8387,8521,"you two used to live in."],[8533,8612,"East... Easton!"]],"46":[[479,667,"This place is where we began."],[1176,1317,"Oh my gosh."],[2331,2448,"It only makes sense"],[2448,2556,"that I end it here."],[3428,3528,"No, Nina!"],[3528,3645,"Please don't take that pill!"],[3691,3774,"Please don't punish"],[3774,3845,"me like this!"],[5146,5330,"No... no..."],[5338,5526,"No no no!"]],"47":[[10,100,"Don't take it!"],[120,190,"Nina!"],[823,1023,"No no no..."],[2063,2130,"Nina?"],[2193,2260,"No..."]],"48":[[4263,4420,"Ever since that day,"],[4520,4650,"Nina vanished like she was"],[4650,4770,"never real to begin with."],[4823,5063,"Not a trace, not a word, nothing."],[5210,5293,"I never learned"],[5293,5373,"what that pill did to her."],[5373,5460,"What kind of scars"],[5460,5633,"it left behind but..."],[5633,5800,"One thing I know for sure,"],[5980,6133,"if she's still alive,"],[6133,6303,"somewhere in this world,"],[6450,6670,"I'll find her. Even if it"],[6670,6900,"takes the rest of my life."]],"49":[[116,296,"I'm sorry, have you"],[296,479,"seen this woman?"],[479,588,"Her name’s Nina Jones,"],[588,704,"she's my wife."],[717,809,"I don't know her."],[809,1034,"Please, just take a look."],[1034,1226,"She’s been missing for weeks, please!"],[2064,2143,"Nina."],[2535,2615,"Here..."],[2648,2740,"Have you seen"],[2740,2861,"this woman? Please..."],[2957,3036,"Nothing..."],[3449,3611,"Thank you anyway."],[3757,3928,"Nina where are you?"],[4158,4291,"Come back to me."],[5467,5676,"Yeah, can you believe it?"],[5697,5868,"That drug I took? Turns out"],[5868,5968,"the side effect was a"],[5968,6097,"total change in appearance."]],"50":[[3,113,"But I heard Easton's"],[113,243,"been out there every day,"],[243,350,"rain or shine,"],[350,516,"tearing the whole damn city"],[516,663,"apart trying to find you."],[673,783,"That has nothing to"],[783,883,"do with me anymore."],[883,1113,"Girl, you two were the couple!"],[1113,1230,"Everyone at school was"],[1230,1330,"obsessed with y’all."],[1330,1590,"Total prom king and queen energy."],[1603,1770,"I never thought he'd cheat."],[1800,1936,"He even came to see me!"],[1936,2110,"You didn't tell him anything right?"],[2110,2223,"Are you kidding?"],[2223,2350,"Hell no."],[2460,2540,"Nina?"],[2593,2800,"Let him drown in his guilt."],[2800,2970,"Let him suffer."],[2970,3050,"Good."],[3103,3373,"I've got a new name, a new face,"],[3383,3506,"a new life."],[3506,3660,"What he does or doesn't regret"],[3660,3823,"has nothing to do with me."],[3920,4010,"Besides,"],[4080,4260,"I'm leaving this place for good."],[4443,4523,"Nina!"]],"51":[[180,300,"Oh, I'm sorry,"],[413,480,"I thought you"],[480,543,"were someone else."],[653,800,"You know, it's weird,"],[890,976,"for a second there, when"],[976,1070,"I was looking at you,"],[1140,1253,"I could have sworn I"],[1253,1373,"was looking at my wife."],[3110,3210,"Nina?"],[4390,4490,"No."],[4700,4793,"No that's just a"],[4793,4950,"coincidence my Nina would..."],[5643,5790,"You won't believe this."],[5820,5923,"This just showed up"],[5923,6010,"at the front desk."],[6100,6310,"No return address."],[6310,6523,"It’s postmarked ten years ago."],[6810,6890,"Ten years ago?"]],"52":[[13,140,"Ten years ago?"],[140,193,"Yeah."],[193,293,"It just showed up at"],[293,400,"the office front desk."],[483,610,"You should open it."],[1843,1930,"What are you writing?"],[2040,2153,"It's a letter,"],[2340,2450,"for us for the future."],[2450,2550,"A letter?"],[2633,2720,"Let me see."],[2760,2956,"No peeking! This one's for"],[2956,3130,"ten years from now, okay?"],[3170,3300,"You have to wait."],[3373,3553,"A letter from my future wife..."],[3553,3760,"I will follow it to the letter."],[3760,3980,"And who says I'm gonna marry you?"],[4130,4213,"Please."],[4303,4420,"10 years from now,"],[4420,4550,"you'll be Mrs Jones."],[4643,4750,"You'll see."],[5023,5130,"Dear Easton."],[5130,5273,"If you're reading this,"],[5273,5343,"it means ten"],[5343,5450,"years have passed."],[5460,5590,"Can you believe it?"],[5623,5753,"Did you keep this letter"],[5753,5853,"safe all this time?"],[5903,5996,"Did you open it at"],[5996,6103,"just the right moment?"],[6163,6326,"I hope we're still together,"],[6326,6470,"side by side like always."],[6570,6710,"But if you're only opening"],[6710,6840,"this because you hurt me..."],[6880,6990,"If you did something"],[6990,7093,"that broke my heart,"],[7143,7290,"then listen closely..."],[7350,7456,"because this letter is"],[7456,7560,"your forgiveness pass."],[7643,7733,"If you're reading"],[7733,7830,"it with real regret..."],[7840,7913,"If your heart"],[7913,8023,"aches even a little..."],[8043,8133,"and your eyes are"],[8133,8233,"stinging with tears..."],[8340,8453,"then maybe..."],[8513,8760,"just maybe... I'll forgive you."]],"53":[[10,123,"Then maybe..."],[180,423,"just maybe... I'll forgive you."],[493,613,"Maybe I'll smile,"],[613,760,"maybe I'll come back."],[783,923,"But future me might"],[923,1073,"be harder to win over."],[1140,1270,"You'll have to bring me flowers,"],[1270,1383,"and take me to the ocean."],[1383,1530,"And remind me every single day"],[1530,1626,"that I'm the only"],[1626,1730,"girl in your world."],[1810,1933,"One last thing..."],[2000,2083,"A wish I folded"],[2083,2180,"between the lines..."],[2253,2346,"That we'll always"],[2346,2440,"walk hand in hand,"],[2440,2546,"through this long"],[2546,2633,"and messy life."],[2660,2816,"and that no storm will"],[2816,2950,"ever tear us apart."],[3013,3276,"With all my love, always,"],[3276,3530,"your future wifey... Nina."],[3620,3830,"I, Easton Jones,"],[3883,3996,"promise to only love you,"],[3996,4100,"for the rest of my life."],[4100,4213,"If I ever lie,"],[4300,4446,"cheat, or break your heart"],[4446,4570,"in any way..."],[4623,4763,"even once..."],[4763,4910,"I walk away with nothing."],[5013,5210,"No money. No excuses."],[5210,5393,"You get everything."],[5540,5793,"You better mean that, cause"],[5793,6050,"if you ever break my heart,"],[6133,6430,"I'll vanish like I was never here."],[6470,6556,"That day is"],[6556,6690,"never coming."],[7293,7473,"No! No! No!"],[8200,8323,"Take me to the airport."]]}